{"tid":566521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不會認錯人？ 雙胞胎兄弟迎娶雙胞胎姊妹","createTime":"2018-02-20T04:21:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T04:43:13.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"52eeab6e6dd771dbb413e4443c6f60efb8cee422","tid":566521,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T04:21:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/20/122110_0cfa16079ca8659a4c8d098159309025.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F20%2F122110_0cfa16079ca8659a4c8d098159309025.png&h=96883d7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕這兩對夫妻怎麼長得一模一樣？34歲的喬許與傑瑞米雙胞胎兄弟（Josh and Jeremy Salyers），去年8月在美國俄亥俄州一個雙胞胎聚會中，巧遇31歲的布列塔尼與布莉安娜姊妹（Brittany and Briana Deane），結果雙雙墜入了愛河，如今這兩對雙胞胎將舉行聯合婚禮！<br />\n據《鏡報》報導，喬許將和布列塔尼結婚，傑瑞米則與布莉安娜牽手。雙胞胎兄弟倆先前在求婚時煞費苦心，特定選在2月2日，剛好象徵著「2對2」。當天雙胞胎姊妺還以為是要拍攝日常影片而已，結果喬許與傑瑞米竟在她們面前單膝下跪。<br />\n布莉安娜說，那真是最神奇的時刻之一，好像在拍電影一樣，她們姊妹和喬許與傑瑞米兄弟就像是靈魂伴侶。這兩對雙胞胎新人將在今年8月，於俄亥俄州特溫斯堡成婚。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2344898\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2344898&d=ERncOCiFAIM0cKEgYWaHRMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=727b6419\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2344898&h=5c0450c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2344898</a>"},{"pid":"fd706c8e9b3ff50f928b8f7f5b7661719f63ee3c","tid":566521,"uid":44291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T04:22:45.000Z","msg":"換妻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2198b81e0f3a0fe8e6e5f94ba93d75bc82be1f88","tid":566521,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd706c8e9b3ff50f928b8f7f5b76617